149
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:22,610
Why are you blaming Lin Ge?

150
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:23,450
Liar!

151
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,440
Don't touch her!

152
00:06:24,730 --> 00:06:25,800
Lin Ge, listen,

153
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:27,210
Feng is your brother.

154
00:06:27,210 --> 00:06:28,830
