176
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,050
Listen,

177
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,170
if you expel Feng, you can let her stay.

178
00:07:12,610 --> 00:07:14,530
Lin Feng can't stay,
and you can't take her away.

179
00:07:19,530 --> 00:07:20,970
I'm having a heart attack.

180
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:24,730
I can't breathe!

181
