♪I'm sad and restless♪

184
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:47,360
♪But I forgive you♪

185
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:50,720
♪I shouldn't have been obsessed with you♪

186
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:54,150
♪Should I leave or stay♪

187
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:56,200
♪I can give up♪

188
00:07:57,530 --> 00:07:58,370
Hello.

189
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,920
Lin Ge, go to the meeting room.

190
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,850
Your grandma is making a scene.

191
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,730
Just give me an answer.

192
00:08:06,170 --> 00:08:08,050
Can you not expel my grandson?

193
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,560
No way.

194
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,440
It's not just

195
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,290
because he tested positive.

196
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,770
He's always slacking off.

197
00:08:13,770 --> 00:08:15,220
He skipped training many times.

198
00:08:15,410 --> 00:08:17,210
No matter how good he is,

199
00:08:17,210 --> 00:08:18,480
I can't let him stay.

200
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,560
I told you

201
00:08:20,170 --> 00:08:21,320
it was Lin Ge's fault!

202
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:23,050
Lin Feng made a mistake.

203
00:08:23,090 --> 00:08:24,050
Lin Ge is innocent.

204
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,090
You can ask Lin Feng

205
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:27,770
how many chances we've given him.

206
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:33,010
Ms. Han, are you saying

207
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:35,200
