216
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,720
I'll compensate you.

217
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:56,440
From now on,

218
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:58,010
I'll give you

219
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,920
half of my allowance every month

220
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:01,370
until I retire.

221
00:09:01,830 --> 00:09:03,170
I'll give you money,

222
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:05,020
and you can feed your grandson.

223
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:06,170
Stop talking nonsense.

224
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:08,170
Pack your things and leave!

225
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:11,960
If I leave,

226
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,890
you can't even get
half of the allowance.

227
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:25,320
Ms. Han, be our witness.

228
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:28,050
My grandson doesn't want to leave.

229
00:09:28,290 --> 00:09:29,770
You forced him to do so!

230
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,890
Don't forget your promise.

231
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:34,850
Wait a minute.

232
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:44,580
From now on,

233
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,250
we're not family anymore.

234
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,840
Remember what you said.

235
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,920
Lin Ge.

236
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,280
Coach, sorry

237
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:01,320
for the trouble.

238
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,360
