239
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,530
Nie Chi, just go.

240
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,890
Let's take a walk.

241
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:39,650
Do you want something sweet?

242
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:42,180
Okay.

243
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:43,060
Hold it.

244
00:10:51,290 --> 00:10:52,130
Sister!

245
00:10:53,890 --> 00:10:54,840
Sister!

246
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:04,320
Sister, are you
the grown-up version of me?

247
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:08,410
Will I be happy when I grow up?

248
00:11:09,050 --> 00:11:11,440
Yes, you'll be happy.

249
00:11:12,130 --> 00:11:13,800
You can skate every day.

250
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:16,770
You can participate in competitions
and earn prizes.

251
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:19,600
Really, I love skating!

252
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,650
Lin Ge, remember,

253
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:26,130
you'll face many difficulties,

254
00:11:26,970 --> 00:11:28,980
but you'll get through them.

255
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:30,650
These experiences

256
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,490
will become

257
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,530
precious memories in your life.

258
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:39,130
What doesn't kill you

259
00:11:40,050 --> 00:11:41,490
makes you stronger.

260
00:11:43,010 --> 00:11:44,200
Lin Ge!

261
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:45,960
Coming!

262
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:51,010
Sister, cotton candy.

263
00:12:09,130 --> 00:12:10,490
I didn't tell you this.

264
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,170
My mom was the only family I had,

265
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,630
but she died a long time ago.

266
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:18,680
I believe she's still with me,

267
00:12:19,530 --> 00:12:22,490
but I can only see her in my dreams
from time to time.

268
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:24,600
I miss her so much.

269
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:26,800
Mom, look!

270
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:28,170
It's so beautiful!

271
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,890
Look at that.

272
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:32,960
Ge, you're one year older.

273
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,680
My dad, my brother,

274
00:12:37,290 --> 00:12:38,840
and my grandma are alive,

275
00:12:39,490 --> 00:12:41,200
but they're not my family.

276
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:43,800
When Lin Feng was five years old,

277
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,490
he had a fever
that turned into pneumonia.

278
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,600
My grandma went crazy.

279
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,880
She said

280
00:12:51,010 --> 00:12:53,320
they couldn't afford to feed two kids.

281
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,600
She asked a man to take me away

282
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,410
behind my mom's back.

283
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,960
She sold you?

284
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:06,200
She said he was our relative,

285
00:13:06,410 --> 00:13:07,600
but who knows?

286
00:13:08,290 --> 00:13:11,320
Fortunately, my mom found out

287
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,410
and stopped him at the railway station.

