00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:14,890
Otherwise,

289
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:18,370
I would've been sent
to a mountainous area

290
00:13:19,010 --> 00:13:20,290
and lived a hard life.

291
00:13:22,770 --> 00:13:23,890
My mom said

292
00:13:24,130 --> 00:13:26,130
she'd take Lin Feng and me away,

293
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,200
but my grandma wouldn't agree.

294
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,560
So, she only took me away.

295
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,890
Didn't your dad stop her?

296
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:38,090
My dad?

297
00:13:38,530 --> 00:13:39,720
He didn't care at all.

298
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:43,130
He didn't even care about Lin Feng,
let alone me.

299
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,800
I don't know where he is.

300
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:50,320
No wonder Lin Feng is always
talking about his grandma.

301
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,560
Sometimes I'm thinking

302
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,720
if my mom had taken Lin Feng away,

303
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,440
would he have...?

304
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:01,680
Never mind.

305
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,890
Life has no turning back.

306
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,800
Since that day,

307
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,200
I've cut ties with them.

308
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:15,200
You went to Jiangnan, right?

309
00:14:18,770 --> 00:14:20,250
Those were

310
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,920
the happiest years of my life.

311
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:27,600
However, my mom died of illness,

312
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:30,370
and I was sent back.

313
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,890
Then I met you.

314
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,920
I've never told you how grateful I am

315
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,670
