316
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,720
If it hadn't been for you,

317
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:47,050
I would've left home,

318
00:14:47,650 --> 00:14:49,550
and my life would've been so miserable.

319
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:55,960
We're even.

320
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,680
What do you mean?

321
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,530
If I hadn't met you

322
00:15:01,010 --> 00:15:02,410
and wanted to defeat you,

323
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:05,370
I wouldn't have kept practicing skating
in Beijing,

324
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:08,320
