met each other again.

325
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:10,770
When we first met,

326
00:15:11,410 --> 00:15:13,440
we changed each other's lives.

327
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,370
We can't choose our blood

328
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:20,130
or our family,

329
00:15:20,650 --> 00:15:22,170
but we can decide which path to follow.

330
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:23,920
Do you know?

331
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:27,890
Actually, I'm not sad.

332
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:30,130
I can finally say goodbye to my past.

333
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,170
I can finally get rid of

334
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,890
my family for good.

335
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:42,130
Is there anything
you want to do right now?

336
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,770
I want

337
00:15:48,010 --> 00:15:49,290
to try my best

338
00:15:50,530 --> 00:15:51,440
to win more competitions

339
00:15:52,890 --> 00:15:54,010
and join the national team.

340
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:57,010
Let's join the national team together and

341
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:58,290
become world champions.

342
00:15:59,050 --> 00:16:01,840
I'll be with you.

343
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:28,970
(When I was little,)

344
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,680
