349
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:51,860
(Now we have a sincere promise.)

350
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:52,820
(Nie Chi)

351
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:54,500
(Happy New Life)

352
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,320
(For our promise.)

353
00:16:57,800 --> 00:17:00,960
(For a brighter future.)

354
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:03,140
