355
00:17:13,730 --> 00:17:15,050
Miss, look around.

356
00:17:15,360 --> 00:17:16,490
You can pick one.

357
00:17:16,730 --> 00:17:17,840
It's on sale.

358
00:17:17,930 --> 00:17:19,840
15 yuan for one, 25 yuan for two.

359
00:17:20,320 --> 00:17:21,530
15 yuan?

360
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:25,130
Do you like it?

361
00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:27,770
