370
00:17:54,800 --> 00:17:56,210
5 yuan online.

371
00:17:56,690 --> 00:17:57,530
It's different.

372
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:58,970
How?

373
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:00,360
Today is different.

374
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,450
