375
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:03,590
For what?

376
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,290
For our promise.

377
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:13,270
Did you buy both of them?

378
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:20,120
