410
00:20:16,970 --> 00:20:17,930
It doesn't matter.

411
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,000
We understand.

412
00:20:19,450 --> 00:20:21,320
If I had such crazy relatives,

413
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,210
I'd cut ties too.

414
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:28,010
Do you have

415
00:20:28,010 --> 00:20:29,450
other family?

416
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:31,770
No.

417
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:35,250
Poor girl.

418
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:37,640
I'm fine.

419
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,480
It's okay.

420
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,730
(Mom)
Hello, Zhu.

421
00:20:41,930 --> 00:20:43,360
Work hard.

422
00:20:46,770 --> 00:20:48,250
