426
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:12,220
(Songbei Province Ice Sports Base)

427
00:21:24,770 --> 00:21:25,970
You must be happy now.

428
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:28,120
Don't get carried away.

429
00:21:28,690 --> 00:21:30,900
Do you still think you were expelled

430
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:32,360
because of me?

431
00:21:32,730 --> 00:21:33,570
Of course.

432
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,490
If you hadn't competed with me

433
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,640
all the time,

434
00:21:36,770 --> 00:21:38,290
I wouldn't have provoked Ms. Han

435
00:21:38,690 --> 00:21:39,640
and ended up like this.

436
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:41,840
I've been hearing
these words all my life.

437
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:43,050
Aren't you tired of it?

438
00:21:44,360 --> 00:21:45,450
Has it ever occurred to you

439
00:21:45,730 --> 00:21:47,210
that you couldn't make progress

440
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:48,970
because your grandma

441
00:21:48,970 --> 00:21:50,600
didn't keep an eye on you?

442
00:21:51,490 --> 00:21:52,800
You're nothing

443
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,840
without your grandma.

444
00:21:54,560 --> 00:21:56,250
Yes, I'm nothing.

445
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,880
You're so ridiculous.

446
00:21:58,260 --> 00:21:59,440
You don't even have a grandma.

447
00:21:59,450 --> 00:22:00,600
No one cares about you.

448
00:22:00,730 --> 00:22:02,050
No one will visit you.

449
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,210
You can't go home.

450
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,770
Oh, no. I'm wrong.

451
00:22:05,170 --> 00:22:06,530
You don't even have a home.

452
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:08,120
What else do you have
except for the team?

453
00:22:08,450 --> 00:22:10,160
You're nothing without the team.

454
00:22:10,210 --> 00:22:11,560
But I'm different.

455
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:13,050
After I leave,

456
00:22:13,050 --> 00:22:15,400
my life will be wonderful.

457
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:16,400
Remember,

458
00:22:16,450 --> 00:22:17,880
from now on,

459
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:21,050
we're not family anymore.

460
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:22,530
I don't want

461
00:22:22,730 --> 00:22:24,120
to see you anymore.

462
00:22:24,490 --> 00:22:25,600
You'd better keep in mind

463
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:27,120
